BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-08-02T03:30:00&endDate=2026-08-03T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Sunday 2 August\, a reduced service will run between Shepherds Bush and Clapham Junction. Trains will use platform 17 at Clapham Junction and will run an uneven service every 15/30 minutes\, with additional Southern Railway services. Southern Railway services will terminate at Shepherd's Bush until 1200
